history.content: I'm a rising senior trying to go for a CS minor. I've already completed CS61A and CS188 with A's and am enrolled in 61B and 61C this semester. It says that you have to have 4+ requirements completed before submitting the application form (which I have to do by Fall 2018 since I'm graduating this Spring) and was wondering if I could submit the application with IP classes or if I have to wait until after finals, or if I am just going to be rejected. Thanks!
history.subject: CS Minor Application with IP classes
